'''大衛·亞歷山大·艾華斯'''（{{lang-en|'''David Alexander Edwards'''}}，{{bd|1986年|2月3日|catIdx=Edwards, David Alexander}}）是一名[[威爾斯|威爾斯]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場_(足球)|中場]]，出身[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]青訓系統，現時效力於[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[謝斯伯利足球俱樂部|梳士貝利]]。

==球會==
===梳士貝利===
艾華斯效力的首間球會是位於他出生地的[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Dave's joy at Premier prospect|url=http://www.shropshirestar.com/2009/04/21/daves-joy-at-premier-prospect/|publisher={{Link-en|什羅普星報|Shropshire Star}}|date=2009-04-21|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2009-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090425103042/http://www.shropshirestar.com/2009/04/21/daves-joy-at-premier-prospect/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並於2003年5月3日首次上陣，但球隊輸給了[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]，更降班至[[英格蘭足球議會聯賽|英格蘭足球議會聯賽]]。

在球隊再次升班後，艾華斯連續三季成為球隊的必然正選，但在一則轉會風波後，他被教練在對[[布里斯托城|布里斯托城]]的升班附加賽決賽中棄用，最終球隊以1-3敗陣，錯失了更上一層樓的機會。<ref>{{cite news|title=Edwards forgives Peters for axe|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/7349965.stm|publisher=[[BBC體育|BBC體育]]|date=2008-04-16|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003070421/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/7349965.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Shrewsbury's finest 2000–10|url=http://www.shropshirestar.com/2010/01/06/shrewsburys-finest-2000-10/#continue|publisher=什羅普星報|date=2010-01-06}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

===盧頓===
2007年6月26日，艾華斯與[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]簽約。<ref>{{cite web| title=Edwards Deal Agreed| work=www.lutontown.co.uk| url=http://www.lutontown.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10372~1082916,00.html| accessdate=2007-08-18}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=Edwards Fee| work=ShrewsWeb| url=http://www.shrewsburytown.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10443~1082950,00.html| accessdate=2007-08-18}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Luton, Shrews end Edwards dispute | work=BBC體育 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/6252902.stm | accessdate=2007-08-04 | date=2007-08-02 | archive-date=2007-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713103513/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/6252902.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

艾華斯為盧頓在英甲上陣了19次，但球隊因財政困難而被扣掉10分。<ref>{{cite news|title=Edwards escapes mad-Hatters party|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-in-wales/2008/01/13/edwards-escapes-mad-hatters-party-91466-20343459/|publisher={{Link-en|南威爾士回聲報|South Wales Echo}}|date=2008-01-13|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009103441/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-in-wales/2008/01/13/edwards-escapes-mad-hatters-party-91466-20343459/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後經過半個球季後以67.5萬鎊轉投狼隊。<ref>{{cite news | title=Wolves complete Edwards transfer | work=BBC體育 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7187990.stm | accessdate=2008-01-16 | date=2008-01-14 | archive-date=2017-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827215901/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7187990.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Edwards' up and downs of 2007|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-in-wales/2008/02/05/edwards-up-and-downs-of-2007-91466-20436626/|publisher=南威爾士回聲報|date=2008-02-05|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009103507/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-in-wales/2008/02/05/edwards-up-and-downs-of-2007-91466-20436626/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===狼隊===
加盟兩天後，艾華斯已在首場代表狼隊的比賽中入球，助球隊以2-0擊敗[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]。<ref>{{cite news | title=Scunthorpe 0-2 Wolves | publisher=BBC體育 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7184739.stm | date=2008-01-19 | accessdate=2013-08-02 | archive-date=2017-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827221229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7184739.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>在這半個球季，艾華斯並未獲得太多上陣機會，直至球隊升級至英超後才獲得正選席位。他在球隊對[[富咸|富咸]]的首場主勝中射入致勝一球，並以2-1取勝。<ref>{{cite news | title=Wolverhampton 2-1 Fulham | publisher=BBC體育 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8257757.stm | date=2009-09-20 | accessdate=2013-08-02 | archive-date=2012-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309101913/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8257757.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>艾華斯在其後兩個球季都受傷患影響，在10/11年只出場了12次，但也在舊梳士貝利隊友[[乔·哈特|-{zh-hans:乔·哈特; zh-hk:祖·赫特;}-]]身上取得了一個入球，助球隊以2-1打敗了[[曼城|曼城]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Wolves-goal-scoring-hero-David-Edwards-says-Joe-Hart-will-be-happy-deep-down-that-he-fired-the-winner-past-him-during-Manchester-City-s-2-1-defeat-article617501.html|title=Wolves hero: Hart will be happy I fired the winner|publisher=[[每日鏡報|每日鏡報]]|date=2010-10-30|access-date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104185904/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Wolves-goal-scoring-hero-David-Edwards-says-Joe-Hart-will-be-happy-deep-down-that-he-fired-the-winner-past-him-during-Manchester-City-s-2-1-defeat-article617501.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在下一個賽季都受腿筋<ref>{{cite news | title=Wolves: Dave Edwards ruled out with hamstring injury | publisher=BBC體育 | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20593620 | date=2012-12-04 | accessdate=2013-08-02 | archive-date=2012-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208061736/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20593620 | dead-url=no }}</ref>和腿部傷患困擾，而碰巧兩次都是在對[[布里斯托城|布里斯托城]]的比賽中受傷。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2013/03/25/wolves-trio-carl-ikeme-bakary-sako-and-dave-edwards-ruled-out-for-the-season/|title=Wolves trio Carl Ikeme, Bakary Sako and Dave Edwards ruled out for the season|publisher=Express & Star|date=2013-03-25|access-date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420032921/http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2013/03/25/wolves-trio-carl-ikeme-bakary-sako-and-dave-edwards-ruled-out-for-the-season/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

艾華斯的合約將於2014年夏季完結。<ref>{{cite news |title=Options taken up |url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/news/article/retained-list-826143.aspx |publisher=狼隊網站 |date=2013-05-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100721195910/http://www.wolves.co.uk/news/article/retained-list-826143.aspx |archivedate=2010-07-21 |accessdate=2013-08-02 }}</ref>2014年6月13日，將重返[[英冠|英冠]]作賽的[[狼隊|狼隊]]與艾華斯簽署一份新的兩年合約，令其留隊至2016年6月底<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27830170 |title=Wolves: Dave Edwards signs new two-year contract at Molineux |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-12-02 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924205040/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27830170 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊==
儘管艾華斯出生在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]，他最終選擇了代表威爾斯國家隊出賽。艾華斯也曾效力威爾斯U17、U19隊，直至在2006年5月16日代表U21隊對塞浦路斯才正式首次在國際賽登場，而翌年11月17日在[[歐洲國家杯|歐洲國家杯]]對陣愛爾蘭的賽事則成為他代表正式國家隊的首次比賽，後備上場，最終比分為2-2。

2008年10月10日，艾華斯在2010世界杯外圍賽對[[列支敦士登國家足球隊|列支敦士登]]的比賽中打開記錄，最終威爾斯憑著他的入球以1-0取勝。他也在2009年6月6日對[[阿塞拜疆國家足球隊|阿塞拜疆]]的賽事中射入一球。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8075370.stm|title=Azerbaijan 0–1 Wales|date=2009-06-06|work=BBC體育|accessdate=2009-06-06|archive-date=2011-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203053538/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8075370.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾華斯再次為威爾斯於2009年11月14日友誼賽中憑[[艾朗·藍斯|艾朗·藍斯]]的助攻攻進一球，以3-0戰勝[[蘇格蘭國家足球隊|蘇格蘭]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Wales 3 Scotland 0 – Diamond victory for Tosh|url=http://www.westerntelegraph.co.uk/archive/2009/11/16/National+Football+%28swa_sport_football_national%29/4740522.Wales_3_Scotland_0_____Diamond_victory_for_Tosh/|publisher={{Lang-en|西部電訊報|Western Telegraph}}|date=2009-11-16|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2018-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210215021/https://www.westerntelegraph.co.uk/archive/2009/11/16/National+Football+%28swa_sport_football_national%29/4740522.Wales_3_Scotland_0_____Diamond_victory_for_Tosh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

